headline: Meet 1 Phenomenal Stock That Would've Made You a Millionaire in the Past. Can It Continue to Climb?
summary: The objective of investing is to raise one's spending power over the long haul.  There's one retail stock that has skyrocketed 53,680% since its initial public offering in April 1993.  Can this stock continue to climb in the years ahead?
